# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic System Checks

This file defines the routine checks to perform during heartbeat polls. Keep these checks efficient and focused on maintaining system health and productivity.

## System Status
- Performance monitoring enabled
- Resource optimization active
- **Memory management**: Compression available on request

## Heartbeat Execution Tasks

